Instead of driving and paying over $1 per litre of fuel in Canada, you could
take the ferry from Bellingham, WA to AK... probably still more expensive but
you go along the "cruise ship" route and see the same scenery as the love boat
etc....and you'll never have to worry about the border guards or hitting a
moose along the way.
